<section id="pricing" class="pricing-section">
  <div class="pricing-container">
    <h2 class="pricing-title">
      Custos simples.<br /><span class="gradient-text"
        >Sem surpresa depois.</span
      >
    </h2>

    <div class="bento-grid">
      <div class="bento-card glass-panel">
        <div class="bento-header">
          <div class="pricing-mode">
            <span class="mode-badge pix">PIX</span>
            <span class="mode-arrow">→</span>
            <span class="mode-badge pix">PIX</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bento-body">
          <div class="pricing-rate">2,49%</div>
          <div class="pricing-desc">por pagamento recebido</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bento-card highlight glass-panel">
        <div class="bento-header">
          <div class="pricing-mode">
            <span class="mode-badge pix">PIX</span>
            <span class="mode-arrow">→</span>
            <span class="mode-badge crypto">Cripto</span>
          </div>
          <span class="pricing-badge">diferencial</span>
        </div>
        <div class="bento-body">
          <div class="pricing-rate">0,5%</div>
          <div class="pricing-desc">sobre o valor convertido</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pricing-notes">
      <p class="pricing-note primary">
        Você só paga quando recebe. Sem mensalidade.
      </p>
      <p class="pricing-note secondary">
        * Pagamentos de <strong>PIX para PIX</strong> têm liberação em 72 horas (política
        da provedora) e exigem chave PIX e dados de contato válidos para eventuais
        consultas.
      </p>
      <p class="pricing-note highlight-note">
        ⚡ <strong>Quer liquidez imediata?</strong> Utilize nosso maior diferencial:
        <strong>PIX para Cripto</strong>, sem saldo preso.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pricing-section {
    padding: 5rem 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .pricing-section {
      padding: 7rem 2rem;
    }
  }

  .pricing-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .pricing-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 2.75rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #fff;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .gradient-text {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff007a 0%, #ff4da6 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .bento-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .bento-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
  }

  .bento-card {
    background: rgba(25, 25, 25, 0.5);
    backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: 28px;
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    text-align: left;
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .bento-card::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(
      180deg,
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03) 0%,
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 100%
    );
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .bento-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px) scale(1.02);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .bento-card:hover::before {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .bento-card.highlight {
    background: linear-gradient(
      145deg,
      rgba(30, 15, 20, 0.8) 0%,
      rgba(20, 10, 15, 0.6) 100%
    );
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 0, 122, 0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(255, 0, 122, 0.08);
  }

  .bento-card.highlight:hover {
    border-color: rgba(255, 0, 122, 0.5);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(255, 0, 122, 0.15);
  }

  .bento-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .bento-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .pricing-mode {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    justify-content: flex-start;
  }

  .mode-badge {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .mode-badge.pix {
    background: rgba(0, 200, 100, 0.12);
    color: #00c864;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 200, 100, 0.2);
  }

  .mode-badge.crypto {
    background: rgba(255, 0, 122, 0.12);
    color: #ff4da6;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 0, 122, 0.2);
  }

  .mode-arrow {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .pricing-rate {
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 6vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #fff;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 8px;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .pricing-badge {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 4px 8px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: rgba(255, 0, 122, 0.15);
    color: #ff4da6;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 0, 122, 0.25);
  }

  .pricing-desc {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
    font-weight: 500;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .pricing-notes {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .pricing-note {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pricing-note.primary {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .pricing-note.secondary {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
    max-width: 90%;
  }

  .pricing-note.secondary strong {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  }

  .pricing-note.highlight-note {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: rgba(255, 0, 122, 0.9);
    background: rgba(255, 0, 122, 0.06);
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 0, 122, 0.2);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .pricing-note.highlight-note strong {
    color: #ff4da6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 479px) {
    .pricing-section {
      padding: 4rem 1rem;
    }

    .bento-card {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .pricing-rate {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
